sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant UserDomain as User (Domain)
    participant DB
    participant Cookie

    Note over Client,Cookie: Phase 1: Initial Login

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    Note right of Client: {email, password}

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(LoginCommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(LoginCommand)

    Handler->>DB: Find user by email
    DB-->>Handler: User found

    Handler->>UserDomain: VerifyPassword(password)
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Compare password hash
    UserDomain-->>Handler: Password valid ✓

    Handler->>UserDomain: Check TwoFactorEnabled
    UserDomain-->>Handler: TwoFactorEnabled = true

    Handler->>Handler: Generate temp token (short-lived)
    Handler-->>Endpoint: Response with requiresTwoFactor

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {requiresTwoFactor: true, sessionToken: "temp_..."}

    Note over Client,Cookie: Phase 2: TOTP Verification

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/auth/2fa/verify
    Note right of Client: {sessionToken, code: "123456"}

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(Verify2FACommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(Verify2FACommand)

    Handler->>DB: Validate temp token
    DB-->>Handler: Token valid ✓

    Handler->>UserDomain: Verify TOTP code
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: TOTP.Verify(code, secret)
    UserDomain-->>Handler: Code valid ✓

    alt Code is valid
        Handler->>Handler: Invalidate temp token
        Handler->>Handler: Generate permanent session
        Handler->>DB: Create session
        DB-->>Handler: Session created ✓

        Handler->>UserDomain: RecordLoginSuccess()
        UserDomain->>UserDomain: Update LastLoginAt
        UserDomain->>UserDomain: Reset FailedLoginAttempts

        Handler-->>Endpoint: LoginResponse
        Endpoint->>Cookie: WriteSessionCookie(permanentToken)
        Cookie-->>Client: Set-Cookie: meepleai_session
        Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK {user, expiresAt}

    else Code invalid
        Handler->>UserDomain: RecordLoginFailure()
        UserDomain->>UserDomain: Increment FailedLoginAttempts

        alt FailedAttempts >= 3
            UserDomain->>UserDomain: LockAccount(15 minutes)
            Handler-->>Client: 429 Too Many Requests
        else
            Handler-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    end
